<!-- RMA, 23/07/09: Redesign of Customer Home workspace(37635).-->
<!-- RMA, 08/10/09: New workspace: Company Customer Home (37635).-->
<!-- RMA, 28/10/09: Fix order of view/title attributes (37635).-->
<!-- RMA, 13/11/09: Layout improvements for demo purposes (37635).-->
<!-- KRN, 09/12/09: Foreign key renamed (38152) -->
<!-- RMA, 13/12/09: Align layouts (37635).-->
<!-- JSV, 01/09/10: Use view AttachDocument_From_Parent on table with documents (38778).-->
<!-- JSV, 02/12/10: Place DocumentRevisions in extension instead of assistant (39187).-->
<!-- BPE, 19/01/11: Embedding the CustomerEntry workspace (39350).-->
<!-- SJK, 07/06/11: Aligning CRM views (39703).-->
